text: Graben, Switzerland is a municipality in the administrative district of Oberaargau in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. ==Villages== Baumgarten, Burach, Gsoll, Hubel, Kleinholz, Schörlishäusern, Schwendi and Stadönz. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Municipalities in Oberaargau
